title: Matsuricon 2008 Dance Audio
description:
This is the dance audio from Matsuricon 2008 in Columbus, OH.
[http://matsuricon.org]

This is the UNCUT-ORIGINAL dance audio w/ MC and some audience. (Live)
Recorded w/ Adobe Audition and rendered as a 320Kbps MP3 File.
File is 4 Hours 57 Minutes and 29 Seconds long.

Featuring:

Draconum (Asst. Tech)
[http://www.draconum.net/]
Breakbeat
Progressive House
(and the $100,000 Pyramid Mix)
 
Oddy (Live Sound Engineer for 2008)
[http://www.0ddmix.com/]
Electro House
Breakbeat
Anime Remixes 
(and the RickRoll Mix)

Jeef (Internal Con Chair for 2008)
Drum and Bass

File and intitial seed by: Lycwolf (Ethan_) [http://lycwolf.com]
